column5: I didn't realize how serious the storm was yesterday for you guys.  I have to go to the airport this aft and I had planned to take my kids to wonderland today or possibly Chuck e cheese/vaughan mills if it was raining.  My question is:  Is everything open or are there streets closed for cleanup etc?
The main streets were cleaned up over night, some side roads are closed.
I came form Rutherford and Islington to Weston Rd this morning everything is fine, Probably some side streets near Mating Grove and 7 are affected.
